item.title: CVE-2022-1914|2024-08-03T00:17:00.972Z -- unknown -- clean-contact
item.description: The Clean-Contact WordPress plugin through 1.6 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack and lead to Stored XSS due to the lack of sanitisation and escaping as well
